WEBVTT

00:00:01.160 --> 00:00:04.976
I really love color.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:08.080
I notice it everywhere and in everything.

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:11.496
My family makes fun of me

00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:15.016
because I like to use colors
with elusive-sounding names,

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:17.176
like celadon ...

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:18.536
(Laughter)

00:00:18.560 --> 00:00:19.760
ecru ...

00:00:21.080 --> 00:00:22.280
carmine.

00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:28.056
Now, if you haven't noticed,
I am black, thank you --

00:00:28.080 --> 00:00:29.096
(Laughter)

00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:31.576
and when you grow up
in a segregated city as I have,